  "text": "Here, relative entropy is used for measuring the divergence of the outputs of two systems fed by the same input data. Posterior probabilities obtained with these models may be inaccurate. Inaccuracy is reduced by combining these posterior probabilities with log-linear interpolation as proposed in [CITATION_1] :",
